panels.description: Inhaltsbezogene Daten: Nur Inhalte, die im ausgewählten Zeitraum veröffentlicht wurden, sind berücksichtigt.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT  CONCAT(REPEAT(" ", $filled_size - CHAR_LENGTH(CAST(ROUND(AVG(Views)) as STRING))), REPLACE(CAST(FORMAT("%'.0f", CAST(ROUND(AVG(Views)) as NUMERIC)) AS STRING), ",", "."))FROM
(
SELECT
time as Datum,
CONCAT(
  CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String)  END ,
  ":",CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String)  END) as Dauer,
  CONCAT(
  CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(DIV(averageViewDuration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(DIV(averageViewDuration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(DIV(averageViewDuration,60) AS String)  END ,
  ":",CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(MOD(averageViewDuration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(MOD(averageViewDuration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(MOD(averageViewDuration,60) AS String)  END) as averageViewTime,
  estimatedMinutesWatched/60 as sehVolumen,
   * FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.youtubeAnalyticsVideos` 
WHERE profileId = $profileID
  AND EXTRACT(DATE from time) BETWEEN DATE('${__from:date}') AND DATE('${__to:date}')
ORDER BY time DESC
)

query.rawSql:
Select a.LRA  FROM
(
SELECT DISTINCT LRA FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.profiles` 
) as a 
ORDER BY(
CASE WHEN a.LRA like  LEFT("${__user.login}",3)
THEN 1
ELSE 0
END
) DESC

SELECT a.profile 
FROM 
(SELECT profile FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.profiles` WHERE LRA = '$LRA' AND youtubeId != 0) as a,
(SELECT  Profil_YT FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.default-settings` WHERE LRA = '$LRA') as b
ORDER BY( 
CASE WHEN a.profile = b.Profil_YT THEN 1
ELSE 2
END
), UPPER(a.profile) ASC

SELECT 
  FORMAT_DATETIME("%e.%m.%Y %n %H:%M Uhr", DATETIME(MAX(last_update),"Europe/Berlin"))  
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.youtube`
WHERE profileId = $profileID

SELECT
CASE
    WHEN date_diff(DATE('${__to:date:iso}'), DATE('${__from:date:iso}'), DAY) = 0 THEN 1
    ELSE date_diff(DATE('${__to:date:iso}'), DATE('${__from:date:iso}'), DAY)
END;
